steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jit011" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit011" display
When I add new column with Name "jitcol011" Type "enum_type" for Table name "jit011"
When I open popup to see column infos Name "jitcol011" of table with Name "jit011"
When I add new item for multi textbox popup Name "Enum Values" with value "jitera01,jitera02,jitera03"
Then I should see multi textbox popup Name "Enum Values" has value "jitera01,jitera02,jitera03"
When I update popup with dropdown Name "Default value" to value "jitera01"
When I press Save button modal popup
When I open popup to see column infos Name "jitcol011" of table with Name "jit011"
When I delete all items of multi textbox popup Name "Enum Values"
